The experimental setup used in our experiment includes: 
- Two scintillation counters S1 and S2; 
- Three plastic scintillation detectors; 
- A set of collimators; 
- A target made of natural tantalum foil with a thickness of 0.1 millimeters located between the first pair of scintillation counters; 
- A trigger system consisting of four scintillation counters T1-T4.

